1
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,199
Is everything ready?

2
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:09,120
To answer the Immortal,

3
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,720
everything is ready in the main hall.

4
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:11,450
Lead the way.

5
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:14,370
Let's go.

6
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:21,579
Please.

7
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,040
Tonight at the Hour of Xu,

8
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:43,160
divide into seven groups,

9
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:43,960
eight people each.

10
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:44,240
Announcing Huaming Road.

11
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:46,160
It must be done before the Hour of Hai.

12
00:02:46,160 --> 00:02:46,600
Yes.

13
00:02:53,079 --> 00:02:55,079
Dry weather and dry things.

14
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:00,760
Be careful with fire.

15
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:06,320
It's the third watch.

16
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:25,079
Sister.

17
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,600
Do you need me for something?

18
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:28,600
I have a question.

19
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:30,250
I don't know if I should ask.

20
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:31,920
Ask away.

21
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:33,520
Are you a monster?

22
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:36,440
What?

23
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,250
Afraid I'll eat you?

24
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,320
No, no, no.

25
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:41,160
I've just never seen

26
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:43,680
such a beautiful and kind monster like you.

27
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:50,079
Little brat.

28
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,040
Sister.

29
00:03:54,040 --> 00:03:54,800
Then what kind of monster are you?

30
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,329
Can you teach me your magic?

31
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:59,120
Sister, please teach me.

32
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:09,920
Master, they are all buried.

33
00:04:38,520 --> 00:04:39,520
Rise.

34
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:57,020
I have set up a barrier in Ercheng.

35
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:58,640
If any monsters enter the city,

36
00:04:58,640 --> 00:04:59,970
I will definitely know.

37
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:00,820
Master.

38
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,920
We've made such a big fuss.

39
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:04,780
What if the monster doesn't come?

40
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:06,560
Don't worry.

41
00:05:06,960 --> 00:05:08,160
The ancestor is here.

42
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:10,000
They'll definitely come.

43
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,360
Don't leave things to chance.

44
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:14,440
This battle is inevitable.

45
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:30,000
This Golden Immortal really looks down on us.

46
00:05:32,080 --> 00:05:32,840
Let's go.

47
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:36,800
Let's teach the High Immortal a good lesson.

48
00:06:15,200 --> 00:06:16,400
You're pretending to sleep.

49
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:18,000
Master, Master!

50
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,280
Come in.

51
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:21,680
You...

52
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,360
What's wrong?

53
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:30,800
The people...

54
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,560
They have all disappeared.

55
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:39,920
What?

56
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:41,970
Why are you here?

57
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:43,360
I...

58
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:44,890
Never mind that.

59
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,280
The people have disappeared.

60
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:47,480
Right.

61
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,800
All the people are gone!

62
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:09,280
Who found out first?

63
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:10,080
I did.

64
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:12,440
It was around the hour of Chen.

65
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,000
I went out for breakfast,

66
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:17,280
only to find none of the shops were open.

67
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:18,480
I searched every house,

68
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,240
and then I realized

69
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:21,160
that everyone in the city had disappeared.

70
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,960
What should we do, Immortal?

71
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:26,010
Ercheng has at least tens of thousands of people.

72
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,040
How could they all disappear overnight

73
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,640
without a trace?

74
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:30,010
It must be a monster.

75
00:07:33,440 --> 00:07:35,400
Such a massive movement of people,

76
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:36,760
yet not a sound.

77
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:38,840
Ancestor,

78
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:41,360
the inescapable net you laid out

79
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:43,760
didn't detect anything either?

80
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:45,159
It seems the intruder...

81
00:07:46,280 --> 00:07:47,640
Not an ordinary person.

82
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:56,760
Hahaha, hahaha.

83
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:01,960
Hahahaha.

84
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:08,640
The rabbit jumps, the dog barks.

85
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:12,920
Silk threads pull, making me smile.

86
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,320
The heart beats.

87
00:08:16,320 --> 00:08:18,000
Chewing in the mouth.

88
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:25,240
Human hearts are like paper for me to manipulate.

89
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:31,880
Why is there no response?

90
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:34,860
Stepping on the positions of the Big Dipper.

91
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:37,600
The Hu family ancestor accompanies me.

92
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:54,480
In such a hurry.

93
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:57,280
The people of Sitiantai are so rude.

94
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:00,960
You didn't even say a word

95
00:09:01,280 --> 00:09:03,160
before taking our people away.

96
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:05,090
Are you fit to speak of manners?

97
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:07,680
Where are the people of Ercheng?

98
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,080
I ate them.

99
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:09,810
Ate them?

100
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:11,400
Ate them? Ate them? Ate them?

101
00:09:11,400 --> 00:09:12,260
What? Ate them?

102
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:13,330
Ate them.

103
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,160
Ate them?

104
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,400
Hahaha.

105
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:19,040
You are so stupid.

106
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:20,560
There are tens of thousands of people in Ercheng.

107
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:21,680
How could I eat them all?

108
00:09:21,680 --> 00:09:23,040
Hahaha.

109
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:23,880
My lord.

110
00:09:24,560 --> 00:09:25,480
You came here

111
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:27,040
to find me.

112
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:29,280
It has nothing to do with the locals.

113
00:09:29,280 --> 00:09:30,880
Don't involve the innocent.

114
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,880
So you are the Golden Immortal.

115
00:09:35,160 --> 00:09:36,960
Your aura seems quite ordinary.

116
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:39,840
Monster, watch your mouth!

117
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:40,640
My master's aura

118
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:43,300
is not something a wild demon like you can judge!

119
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:46,280
A wild demon?

120
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:49,090
You're courting death!

121
00:09:58,400 --> 00:09:59,840
Now that's some aura.

122
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:00,800
It seems

123
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:04,000
you don't intend to let the people go easily.

124
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,000
What do you think?

125
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:45,130
Bullying the few with the many?

126
00:10:58,880 --> 00:11:00,240
I'd like to see,

127
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:02,120
before you kill me,

128
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:03,740
how many people I can kill.

129
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:16,320
Do you not care about the lives of the people?

130
00:11:16,320 --> 00:11:17,880
Wild monster,

131
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:20,080
don't underestimate us.

132
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:49,640
Found it.

133
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:51,560
Save them.

134
00:11:51,880 --> 00:11:52,940
There are too many.

135
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,010
I need some time.

136
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,720
Slay the demons first.

137
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:01,640
Jinwang.

138
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:08,320
Pingjie Qianghaihui.
